Paper: hep-th/9506171

Date: 1995-06-26

Title: The Small Scale Structure of Space-Time

Comments: 50 pages, TeX (two references added)

This essay is a tour around many of the lesser known pregeometric models ofphysics, as well as the mainstream approaches to quantum gravity, in search ofcommon themes which may provide a glimpse of the final theory which must liebehind them.